snippet.title: Meet GARTIC SHOW!  - The new game for STREAMERS!
snippet.description:
Stream now: https://gartic.show

Play with your audience with Gartic Show! A game made for streamers to bring more interactivity and engagement to their live streams.

It's easy to set up and 100% free!
